cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about image inpainting using deep generative models, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The proposed method involves encoding contextual semantics and attention transfer, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the use of pyramid-context encoder and multi-scale decoder can be considered as graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research, respectively.
